OL,5, Hundreds of thousands of North Koreans 
OL,6, may be exposed to radioactive materials
OL,7, creeping into water, a non-governmental
OL,8, organisation based in Seoul says.      
OL,10,FThis is also a risk to people in China,
OL,11,FSouth Korea and Japan, the Transitional
OL,12,FJustice Working Group says.            
OL,14,FThe group is urging South Korea to     
OL,15,Foffer radiation exposure tests for     
OL,16,Fdefectors who have lived near          
OL,17,FNPunggye-ri, the North's main nuclear  
OL,18,Fsite.                                  
OL,20,FIt estimates that up to 540,000        
OL,21,Fresidents may be at risk.              
